22,3,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;22,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;401 Unauthorized&lt;/code&gt;: Missing or invalid Auth token.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;22,4,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;22,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;409 Conflict&lt;/code&gt;: Business logic conflict (e.g., product went out of stock during processing).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;22,5,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;22,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;429 Too Many Requests&lt;/code&gt;: Rate limit exceeded.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr data-path-to-node=&quot;23&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;24&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;5. Idempotency Handling&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;25&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;To prevent duplicate orders caused by network retries, the &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;25&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;59&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;POST /v1/orders&lt;/code&gt; endpoint requires a unique &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;25&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;102&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;25&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;102&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Idempotency-Key&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in the header.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;26&quot; style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 32px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;26,0,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;26,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Server side:&lt;/b&gt; The key is stored in a distributed cache (like Redis) for 24 hours.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;26,1,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;26,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;First Request:&lt;/b&gt; Processed normally; result is cached with the key.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;26,2,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;26,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Subsequent Request:&lt;/b&gt; If the key exists, the server returns the cached response immediately without re-processing the payment or inventory decrement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;hr data-path-to-node=&quot;27&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;28&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;6. Rate Limiting Strategy&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;29&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;We implement a &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;29&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;15&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Leaky Bucket&lt;/b&gt; algorithm to smooth out bursts of traffic.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;30&quot; style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 32px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Tiered Limits:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,1&quot; style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 32px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,1,0,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,1,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Users:&lt;/b&gt; 100 requests per minute (RPM) for order creation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,1,1,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Public/Guest:&lt;/b&gt; 20 RPM for stock checks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,1,2,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;30,0,1,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Internal Services:&lt;/b&gt; 5000 RPM (Service-to-Service).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Headers:&lt;/b&gt; Every response includes rate limit metadata:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,1&quot; style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 32px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,1,0,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,1,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;X-RateLimit-Limit&lt;/code&gt;: Max requests allowed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,1,1,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;X-RateLimit-Remaining&lt;/code&gt;: Requests left in current window.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,1,2,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;30,1,1,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;X-RateLimit-Reset&lt;/code&gt;: Time until the limit resets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr data-path-to-node=&quot;31&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;32&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;7. API Security &amp;amp; Resilience&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;33&quot; style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 32px; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;33,0,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;33,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;JWT Authentication:&lt;/b&gt; All order-related endpoints require a Bearer token.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;33,1,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;33,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Pagination:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;33,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;12&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;GET /v1/orders&lt;/code&gt; uses cursor-based pagination (&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;33,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;57&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;?cursor=xyz&amp;amp;limit=20&lt;/code&gt;) to handle large order histories without memory spikes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;33,2,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;33,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Circuit Breaker:&lt;/b&gt; If the Inventory service is down, the Order service fails fast with a &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;33,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;87&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;503 Service Unavailable&lt;/code&gt; instead of hanging.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1810" width="560" x="220" y="300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
